Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Available as a whole or separately

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
• Split over high clearance warehousing, ‘cross dock’ facility, general warehousing, hardstand and modern office space
• Corporate office and amenities spaces in each building
• B-Double access to Jervois Street and adjoining Ashwin Parade
• Extensive hardstand areas available with efficient truck access to a total of 21 roller doors on site  
• Superb loading weather protection with large canopies throughout the site
• Can be leased as entire offering or as individual sites
• Total built area of 15,212 sqm* can accommodate even the largest interstate transport or parcel handling businesses with options for client 3PL
• Perfect for 3PL, E-Commerce, and Couriers with a uniquely central location for sorting parcels for same day delivery north, south and the CBD with accompanying high clearance warehouse space
• Available due to Cochrane’s Transport relocating to new purpose built premises
. Expected availability Qtr 2/3 2020
. Phone sole agents CBRE to inspect

Torrensville continues to be a sought-after industrial area, driven by its central position and connectivity to the Adelaide CBD, Adelaide Airport and Port Adelaide. 

Be situated amongst major industrial users in this highly sought location with close proximity to South Road, Port Road, newly developed North-South motorway and the soon to be completed Northern Connector. 

Excellent amenity with walking distance to the new Brickworks Marketplace development and adjacent River Torrens Linear Park

Unique in its scale and diversity, this is a very rare opportunity to position your operation ahead of your competitors

*approximately

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: TORRENSVILLE TRANSPORT AND WAREHOUSING ‘SUPER SITE’ – AVAILABLE AS A WHOLE OR SEPARATELY

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
• Ground and first floor modern office space and amenities of 200 sqm* plus additional refurbished character offices of 522sqm* available to the corner of Ashwin and Jervois Street
• Two high clearance warehouses of 1,440 sqm* and 2,535 sqm* to total 3,975sqm*
• Warehouse span clearance ranging between 7.1m to 7.5m*
• B-Double access via Jervois Street and exiting to Ashwin Parade
• Two large canopy areas of 1,930 sqm* and 807 sqm* to enable all weather undercover loading
. Solar PV array that services two meters  
• Perfect for 3PL, E-Commerce, and Couriers with a uniquely central location for sorting parcels for same day delivery north, south and the CBD
• The building has cross-dock capability
• Available due to Cochrane’s Transport relocating to new purpose built premises
• Pitstop Café tenancy excluded
• Phone sole agents CBRE to inspect
